                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">STORAGE <br/>
                     </content>Store at room temperature 15° to 25°C (59° to 77°F); avoid freezing and excessive heat above 40°C (104°F).</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Manufactured by: <br/>Actavis Laboratories UT, Inc.<br/>Salt Lake City, UT 84108 USA </paragraph>
